### CramBrain API Smoke Tests
### Run these tests against your deployed API

@baseUrl = https://your-render-app.onrender.com
@localUrl = http://localhost:8000

### Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/health

### Get Presigned Upload URL
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/presign
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "test.pdf"
}

### Ingest Document (replace with actual file_url from presign response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "file_url": "https://your-bucket.your-domain.com/docs/test.pdf",
  "original_name": "test.pdf"
}

### Ask Question (replace with actual doc_id from ingest response)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "query": "What is this document about?",
  "doc_id": "your-doc-id-here",
  "top_k": 6
}

### Generate Quiz (replace with actual doc_id)
POST {{baseUrl}}/v1/quiz
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "doc_id": "your-doc-id-here",
  "topic": "general content",
  "n": 10
}

### List Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/docs

### Get Document Details (replace with actual doc_id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/docs/your-doc-id-here

### Search Documents
GET {{baseUrl}}/v1/search?q=test&limit=10

### Test with Local API
GET {{localUrl}}/v1/health
